lead_paragraph: Angelique Kerber picked the perfect time to earn her first win over Victoria Azarenka, outgunning the big-hitting Belarusian 6-3 7-5 on Wednesday to advance to her first Australian Open semi-final.

headline.print_headline: Kerber Thwarts Azarenka Comeback to Reach Semi-Finals
